::DarkMouse::

She looked at Dracona laying on the table and waiting for her to come 
out her drugged sleep.  She thought about how this all looked so 
familiar to her.  Something in her felt pity for the bot laying there.
She felt something else too.  Like da-ja-voe almost.  She couldn't 
help it.  She stared at the Dracona.  She mumbled something about how 
this looked so familiar.  She turned and went to seek Scorponok's 
help.  He knew the answers to the questions brewing in her mind.
